The paper discusses a system for workload analysis and management for multi-tenant and multi-database platforms, which is a core topic in database systems (cs.DB). The proposed system relies on learned vector embeddings for SQL queries, which is a common technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses potential applications for workload analysis, including security audits (cs.CR) and user behavior modeling (cs.SE).
